4-6`, `sonnet-4-5`, `haiku-4-5`\n- Full version aliases: `claude-opus-4-6`, `claude-sonnet-4-6`, etc.\n- [1m] suffix: All models support `[1m]` suffix for 1M context when compatible\n\n**Agent Model Examples:**\n- `grok`, `grok-code`, `grok-code-fast-1` → `opencode/grok-code`\n- `nemotron-3-super-free` → `opencode/nemotron-3-super-free`\n- `glm-5-free`, `deepseek-r1-free` → Kilo gateway models\n- Full provider syntax: `opencode/model-name`, `kilo/model-name`\n\n**Codex Models:**\n- `gpt-5`, `gpt-5.4`, `gpt-5.4-mini`, `gpt-5.3-codex`, `o3-mini`\n\nThis centralized system in `/src/models/index.mjs` ensures consistent model handling across all tools and provides extensive validation, fuzzy matching, and helpful error messages."
