[2026-04-17T05:27:17.092Z] [INFO]         "text": "All done. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n**PR**: https://github.com/link-assistant/hive-mind/pull/1621\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`src/models/index.mjs`** — Updated `opus` alias to `claude-opus-4-7`, added `opus-4-7` and `claude-opus-4-7` aliases, added Opus 4.7 to `MODELS_SUPPORTING_1M_CONTEXT`, kept `opus-4-6`/`claude-opus-4-6` for backward compatibility.\n\n2. **`src/config.lib.mjs`** — Updated comment to reflect `opus` now maps to Opus 4.7. `isOpus46OrLater` already supported the `opus-4-7` pattern.\n\n3. **`tests/test-opus-47-model-support.mjs`** — New test file with 41 tests covering all Opus 4.7 functionality.\n\n4. **Updated existing tests** — Fixed assertions in 3 test files where `opus` alias tests expected `claude-opus-4-6` (now `claude-opus-4-7`). All 193 tests pass.\n\n5. **`docs/case-studies/issue-1620/README.md`** — Case study documenting Opus 4.7 specs, breaking API changes, implementation plan, and sources.\n\n6. **Version bump** — `1.51.0` -> `1.52.0`."
